{"tid":1537782,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"讀中大嘅同我入黎","createTime":"2019-09-04T04:57:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T05:48:01.000Z","uid":257506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"902008b5e20534eda3d490115037bf0552a4b04d","tid":1537782,"uid":257506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:57:45.000Z","msg":"其實你地知唔知咩叫罷課，好似雨革咁 罷課係出去靜坐，起碼話比人聽有呢個人數起到。<br />\n雖說學生會有搞個罷課行程表，DLLM琴日嘅練武得小貓三四隻，9月2日開學禮d人呢？？我相信果到唔係全部罷課嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n話就話暴大，發夢就得，唔上堂就唔得？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以我現在呼籲所有中大人立即投入罷課</span></span><br />\n<br />\n加上<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">由於要比同路人發現大家嘅聲音+<strong>乜行動都無嘅話，罷課同走堂無分別</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">所以，由即日起所有中大罷課人士於課程時間內，起百萬大道集合(除非官方發放其他消息)，直至死線</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecd68a3e9ca8f0a2578760dbe2e379e3e8f8b5dd","tid":1537782,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:57:51.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"799580c4fccb16eaff36257c0845998991f42d4d","tid":1537782,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:00:50.000Z","msg":"Add drop period前都咁積極上堂嘅人真係唔知咩心態"},{"pid":"b263b090805f662c17916b5a205503a87aea6255","tid":1537782,"uid":257506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:06:12.000Z","msg":"自推10連"},{"pid":"dc3bacd06da4343f24ba7a58772cbbfb52306d02","tid":1537782,"uid":257506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:06:22.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"14ffe2f0598d00e39bf60281fcfce597d1b1f8d6","tid":1537782,"uid":257506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:06:32.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"e4c4870db391b14650de155eb22d255479be7aa2","tid":1537782,"uid":257506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:06:43.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"43ac496e1c0b766555a27b2fedf086ac30fe94bf","tid":1537782,"uid":257506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:06:53.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"3b373838a12006f2f37f86f609564e335824071c","tid":1537782,"uid":257506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:07:05.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"d4f46c28e49bc5950445c6d44eabc64ae0b01835","tid":1537782,"uid":257506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:07:15.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"9cadd84c264da4dbd96e8fc8ae4ec0c897e98cea","tid":1